N(NH1, NH2, t)
N(NH, H, t)
N(H, NH, t)
N(H1, H2, t)
N(H,NH,t) = 1 + \sum_{i=1}^{t} \sum_{j=1}^{i} \left(\frac{g-c+b\cdot((i-j)\cdot(g-c)/2)}{2}\right)^j
N(H, NH, t=0) = 1
N(H, NH, t=1) = 1 + \frac{g-c}{2}
N(H, NH, t=2) = 1 + \frac{g-c}{2} + \frac{g-c + b\cdot\frac{g-c}{2}}{2} + \left(\frac{g-c}{2}\right)^2
